resources.string:
Step 1: Please make sure that the device is successfully connected to the built-in Bluetooth of your phone and is within close proximity;
 Step 2: Ensure that the device is powered on (the headphones need to be taken out of the case) so that everyLink Voice can search for and associate with the device;
 Step 3: Check if everyLink Voice has been granted Bluetooth and local network permissions by the system;
 Step 4: After confirming the above steps, you can click Retry to initiate the association again.
